## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="988e2-102"><xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions>类提供和<xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions.DontFragment%2A>属性以控制 Internet 控制消息协议 (ICMP) 回显请求数据包的传输方式。 <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions.Ttl%2A></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="988e2-102">The <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions> class provides the <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions.Ttl%2A> and <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions.DontFragment%2A> properties to control how Internet Control Message Protocol (ICMP) echo request packets are transmitted.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="988e2-103">属性为<xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.Ping>类发送的数据包指定生存时间。 <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions.Ttl%2A></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="988e2-103">The <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions.Ttl%2A> property specifies the Time to Live for packets sent by the <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.Ping> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="988e2-104">此值指示在丢弃<xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.Ping>数据包之前可以转发该数据包的路由节点数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="988e2-104">This value indicates the number of routing nodes that can forward a <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.Ping> packet before it is discarded.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="988e2-105">如果要测试将数据包从源计算机发送到目标计算机所需的转发数 (也称为 "跃点"), 则设置此选项非常有用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="988e2-105">Setting this option is useful if you want to test the number of forwards, also known as hops, are required to send a packet from a source computer to a destination computer.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="988e2-106"><xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions.DontFragment%2A>属性控制发送到远程主机的数据是否可以分为多个数据包。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="988e2-106">The <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions.DontFragment%2A> property controls whether data sent to a remote host can be divided into multiple packets.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="988e2-107">如果要测试用于传输数据包的路由器和网关的最大传输单位 (MTU), 此选项很有用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="988e2-107">This option is useful if you want to test the maximum transmission unit (MTU) of the routers and gateways used to transmit the packet.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="988e2-108"><xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.Ping.Send%2A> <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.Ping.SendAsync%2A> <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions> <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingReply.Options%2A>类的实例将传递给<xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingReply>和方法, 类通过属性返回的实例。 <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="988e2-108">Instances of the <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions> class are passed to the <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.Ping.Send%2A> and <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.Ping.SendAsync%2A> methods, and the <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingReply> class returns instances of <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions> via the <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingReply.Options%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="988e2-109">有关实例<xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions>的初始属性值的列表, <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions.%23ctor%2A>请参见构造函数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="988e2-109">For a list of initial property values for an instance of <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions>, see the <xref:System.Net.NetworkInformation.PingOptions.%23ctor%2A> constructor.</span></span>  
  
   
  
